<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:09:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与内塔尼亚胡会面前一天，特朗普表示以色列需要“快速”结束加沙战争，夺回人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</link><description>这位前总统还批评了那些抗议以色列总理在美国国会演讲的人，呼吁以亵渎美国国旗的罪名判处一年监禁</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</guid></item><item><title>利伯曼说，拒绝加入以色列军队的极端正统派应该获得犯罪记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</link><description>以色列前国防部长阿维格多·利伯曼表示，“一名真正的正统派士兵——而不是冒充正统派的人——在以色列国防军服役是没有问题的。”他认为，极端正统派可以留在自己的社区内，同时接受世俗教育或征兵。到军队</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部警方延长对被控杀害 6 岁儿子的妇女的拘留期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</link><description>上周，嫌疑人在一家商场袭击并打伤一名保安后被捕。几个小时后，她儿子的祖母在家里的公寓里发现了他的尸体，上面有暴力痕迹。邻居过去曾就她的行为向警方报告过</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在恐怖袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-terror-ramming-attack/00000190-ea2b-d298-a592-fa3b3a0b0000</link><description>来自 Pardes Hannah-Karkur 的 24 岁阿里尔·托帕兹 (Ariel Topaz) 在 7 月初的恐怖袭击中受重伤，于周三死亡。他的母亲写道：“即使进行了所有的祈祷，不幸的是，下一个‘公告’是我的整个世界，我亲爱的儿子，我的爱丽儿”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-terror-ramming-attack/00000190-ea2b-d298-a592-fa3b3a0b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和内塔尼亚胡的讲话展现出最鲜明和最黑暗的对比</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-netanyahus-speeches-showed-up-the-starkest-and-darkest-of-contrasts/00000190-e9c8-d541-adbc-f9f8fd9e0000</link><description>乔·拜登和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡之间在风格和实质上的差异在周三的演讲中最为明显。这是恩典与受害、真相与谎言、真实与虚假、真实与虚假的案例</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:28:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-netanyahus-speeches-showed-up-the-starkest-and-darkest-of-contrasts/00000190-e9c8-d541-adbc-f9f8fd9e0000</guid></item><item><title>演讲内容有真实性吗？嗯，这确实是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-25/ty-article-podcast/was-there-anything-authentic-about-the-speech-well-it-was-authentically-netanyahu/00000190-e9a7-d45d-a5b3-ebaf4c450000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:22:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-25/ty-article-podcast/was-there-anything-authentic-about-the-speech-well-it-was-authentically-netanyahu/00000190-e9a7-d45d-a5b3-ebaf4c450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队报告三名以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸高速公路枪击事件中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</link><description>士兵们在绿线西岸城市盖勒吉利亚附近的 55 号高速公路上行驶时被枪杀。士兵们的情况为中度和轻症，被疏散到卡法萨巴的梅尔医院。军方表示，目前正在搜寻枪手</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府敦促最高法院驳回巴勒斯坦权力机构针对恐怖受害者赔偿法的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</link><description>7月初，巴勒斯坦权力机构首次向以色列法院提出请愿，要求以色列法院驳回允许恐怖袭击受害者起诉巴勒斯坦权力机构要求赔偿的以色列议会法律。以色列政府要求法院驳回请愿书，称巴勒斯坦权力机构向恐怖分子及其家人支付报酬</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院声明：解释为何本格维尔部的非法枪支许可证尚未被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</link><description>以色列高等法院正在审理一份请愿书，要求废除 12,000 多张枪支许可证，因为本-格维尔的部门显然没有遵循程序并非法发放枪支许可证</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔在联盟协议中控制了西岸非法建设执法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</link><description>在正统派和本格维尔就另一项授权拉比理事会有权使用手机的法律达成协议后，以色列议会通过了这项将权力从斯莫特里奇转移到本格维尔的法律。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四会见拜登和哈里斯，因为美国要求结束加沙战争的压力越来越大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</link><description>人质家属预计将出席白宫会议。除了释放人质的努力外，美国还向内塔尼亚胡寻求有关停止战斗和加沙战后计划的最新信息。内塔尼亚胡周五还将在特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园会见特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚制裁参与西岸针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为的七名以色列定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</link><description>澳大利亚的声明称，一些以色列人参与了性侵犯和性虐待。制裁还针对“山顶青年”，此举将使未来能够对参与袭击巴勒斯坦人的非法前哨定居者采取更广泛的行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</guid></item><item><title>全文：内塔尼亚胡 2024 年向国会发表的讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙没有最终结果并脱离现实，内塔尼亚胡的雄辩无法赢得对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡声称人质的命运如此紧迫，他就不会再次推迟卡塔尔谈判的恢复；与总理关系密切的人士称他的讲话具有历史意义，但以色列人专注于救回人质，而美国人则专注于选举</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙南部丧生的以色列士兵的姓名，另有两人受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</link><description>特朗普在接受福克斯新闻采访时表示，以色列必须“快速”结束加沙战争 ■ 据报道，英国将撤回对国际刑事法院逮捕内塔尼亚胡、加兰特的请求的反对 ■ 以色列国防军找到了 10 月 7 日被杀并被带到加沙的五名以色列人的尸体 ■ 内塔尼亚胡会见拜登哈里斯在美国要求结束加沙战争的压力越来越大的情况下 ■ 以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，等待拜登和内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论后离开</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会的空洞“胜利”：在演讲中获胜，在战争中失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hollow-triumph-in-congress-winning-in-speeches-losing-in-wars/00000190-e668-d8b8-a59a-eefeb7e90000</link><description>哈斯巴拉的陈词滥调、空洞的承诺、兴高采烈的共和党人：内塔尼亚胡的讲话脱离了战时现实 — — 也脱离了以色列人</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hollow-triumph-in-congress-winning-in-speeches-losing-in-wars/00000190-e668-d8b8-a59a-eefeb7e90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前往华盛顿并不是为了结束加沙战争。他去寻找延长时间的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-go-to-washington-to-end-gaza-war-he-went-to-get-the-means-to-prolong-it/00000190-e68a-d6e6-afde-e6df058e0000</link><description>虽然更多的以色列人质尸体被发现，但内塔尼亚胡不仅寻求美国武器的支持，而且还寻求以色列对加沙地带的永久控制</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-go-to-washington-to-end-gaza-war-he-went-to-get-the-means-to-prolong-it/00000190-e68a-d6e6-afde-e6df058e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会表示，以色列不会重新安置加沙，抨击校园抗议者是伊朗“有用的白痴”，并呼吁建立区域联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-wont-resettle-gaza-campus-protesters-are-irans-useful-idiots/00000190-e64a-d541-adbc-fffa7c6e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中呼吁美国继续武装以色列，以便以色列能够“更快地完成任务”，但没有提及加沙停火和人质协议。六名人质亲属因抗议被带出会议厅并被捕</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-wont-resettle-gaza-campus-protesters-are-irans-useful-idiots/00000190-e64a-d541-adbc-fffa7c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队在汗尤尼斯行动中找到了被带到加沙的五名以色列人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israel-recovers-body-of-maya-goren-kidnapped-on-oct-7-and-killed-in-captivity/00000190-e656-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</link><description>以色列军队表示，本周在汗尤尼斯发动的袭击（据报道有 70 名巴勒斯坦人被杀）的主要目标之一是打捞人质的尸体</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israel-recovers-body-of-maya-goren-kidnapped-on-oct-7-and-killed-in-captivity/00000190-e656-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔推动立法让他控制以色列国民警卫队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</link><description>一位知情人士告诉《国土报》，极右翼国家安全部长的决议草案“试图建立一支由他控制的安全部队”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</guid></item></channel></rss>